<title xml:lang="gez" type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1395Fethan#IntroductionCanons">Table of contents</title>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="p1_i1.3">
<locus from="6r"/>
<title xml:lang="en" type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1395Fethan#Part1">The first part <foreign xml:lang="gez">
ክፍል፡ ቀዳማዊ፡</foreign> Ecclesiastical law</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">አንቀጽ፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ በእንተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወዘይደሉ፡ ላቲ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="p1_i1.4">
<locus from="66r"/>
<title xml:lang="en" type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1395Fethan#Part2">The second part <foreign xml:lang="gez">
ክፍል፡ ዳግማዊ፡</foreign> Civil law</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">አንቀጽ፡ ፳ወ፫፡ በእንተ፡ መብልዕ፡ ወአልባስ፡ ወማኅደር፡ ወተግባረ፡ እድ፡ ዘይደሉ፡ ለመሲሐውያን።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="p1_i1.5">
<locus from="144v"/>
<title xml:lang="en" type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1395Fethan#Appendix">Supplementary part on the law of inheritance</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">አንቀጽ፡ ተዋርሶ፡ ዘተሰነዓዉ፡ ላዕሌሁ፡ እግዚእነ፡ አባ፡ ቂርሎስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘእለ፡ እስክንድርያ፡
  ምስለ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶሳቲሁ፡ ወሊቃናቲሁ፡ ወመኳንንቲሁ፡ ወውእቱ፡ ፷ምዕራፍ፡ ወመብዝኅቱኒ፡ እምነ፡ ዘጸሐፎ፡ አባ፡ ቆዝምስ፡ ፩እምሊቃነ፡
  ጳጳሳት፡ ዘእለ፡ እስክንድርያ። ወይቤ፡ በተፍጻሜቱ፡ ከመ፡ ውእቱ፡ እምዘ፡ ሠርዕዎ፡ እምሊቃነ፡ ሕግ፡ ወተረፈ፡ ዚአሁ፡ እምልብ፡ ወዘልማድ፡
  ወዝንቱ፡ ተሠርዓ፡ አመ፡ ዓሡሩ፡ ወሰቡዑ፡ ለወርኃ፡ መስከረም፡
  በ<date calendar="diocletian" when="0958">፱፻፶ወ፰ዓመተ፡ ሰማዕታት፡</date> ንጹሓን፡ ትንብልናሆሙ፡ ተሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ አሜን። </incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

<colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
<locus target="#147v"/>
መልአ፡ ጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ቀኖና፡ ዘፍትሐ፡ ኵነኔ፡ ሕግ፡ መሲሓዊት፡ በዕለተ፡ ረቡዕ፡ አመ፡ ፩ለጥቅምት፡
<date calendar="world" when="7172">በ፸፻ወ፩፻፸ወ፪ዓመተ፡ ዓለም፤</date> ወተፈጸመ፡ በዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ በ፳አብቅቴ፡ በ፳ወ፪ሠርቀ፡ ሌሊት፡ ወ፩ሠርቀ፡
መዓልተ:<gap reason="omitted" resp="PRS10171Wright"/> ወበ፲አርባዕቱ፡ ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቱ፡
ለንጉሠ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወለእግዚአብሔር፡ አኰቴት፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለም። ወዘአዕለዋ፡ ኅፁፅ፡ ወኃጥእ <gap reason="omitted" resp="PRS10171Wright"/>
ወዘአጽሐፋኒ፡<gap reason="omitted" resp="PRS10171Wright"/>ወልደ፡ አቡነ፡ ትክለ ሃይማኖት፡
<note>The colophon states that the manuscript was written in the 14th year of the reign of
king <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10375Yohanne">Yoḥannǝs</persName> i. e. 1681.</note>
<note>The colophon has been altered by various erasures and corrections, from the words
<foreign xml:lang="gez">በ፸፻ወ፩፻፸ወ፪</foreign> (originally <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወ፬) ዓመተ፡ ዓለም፡</foreign> to the
 words <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወ፬ሠርቀ፡ መዓልት፡</foreign> after which three lines have been erased.
The rest has been left untouched, with the exception of the name of the owner, which
has disappeared on <locus target="#148r">f. 148r</locus>, as well as on <locus target="#2r">f. 2r</locus>.</note>
</colophon>
</msItem>
